source: Add directory structure to Media entities.
Allows uploading files through one upload field. A media type is identified by it's file extension(s)!
As this field only accepts one media, only the first one uploaded is selected.
By checking this option, Root directory will show all the files.
Choose from pre-defined image styles or set custom dimensions.
Create taxonomy vocabulary to hold directory structure and select it in the settings.

Enables simplified upload form, where user can upload different file types through one upload field.
Here you'll find settings regarding the CKEditor integration.
If checked, the Add Media menu links of admin_toolbar_tools will be hidden and also it's Media and Files links depending on the tab settings. . Needs manual cache rebuild!
If checked, the Files tab will be hidden. Needs manual cache rebuild!
If checked, the Media tab will be hidden. Needs manual cache rebuild!
In this dialog you are only allowed to change the source language of medias having no translation yet.
